<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"/>
<title>Bookstore</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="../css/style.css" rel="stylesheet"/></head>
<body>
<main class="container">
<a href="#" class="general-back-link">
<i class="fa fa-long-arrow-left mr-15"></i>Back to results</a>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-sm-6">
<div class="product-gallery">
<div class="mb-20"><%= image_tag(@book.image, :alt => "rss feed", :class => "img-responsive") %></div>
<div class="images clearfix">
<a href="#" class="img-link"><%= image_tag(@book.image, :alt => "rss feed", :class => "img-responsive") %></a>
<a href="#" class="img-link"><%= image_tag(@book.image, :alt => "rss feed", :class => "img-responsive") %></a>
<a href="#" class="img-link"><%= image_tag(@book.image, :alt => "rss feed", :class => "img-responsive") %></a></div></div></div>
<div class="col-sm-6">
<h1 class="mt-res-0"><%= @book.title %></h1>
<p class="lead small"><%= @book.author %></p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<p class="h1 in-gold-500 mt-10">€<%= @book.price %></p></div>
<div class="col-xs-5 col-md-3">
<div class="input-group general-position">
<a href="#" class="input-link">
<i class="fa fa-minus line-height-40"></i></a>
<input type="text" class="form-control quantity-input"/>
<a href="#" class="input-link">
<i class="fa fa-plus line-height-40"></i></a></div></div>
<div class="col-xs-7 col-md-5">
<a href="/add_item?add_item=<%= @book.id %>">
<button id = "book-add-to-cart" class="btn btn-default pull-right general-position">Add to Cart</button></a></div></div>
<div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
<p>Description</p>
<p class="lead small line-height-2"><%= @book.description %>
<a href="#" class="in-gold-500 ml-10">Read More</a></p></div>
<div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
<div class="clearfix">
<p class="pull-left">Year of publication</p>
<p class="lead small pull-right"><%= @book.year %></p></div></div>
<div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
<div class="clearfix">
<p class="pull-left">Dimensions</p>
<p class="lead small pull-right">H:<%= @book.height %>" x W: <%= @book.width %>" x D: <%= @book.depth %></p></div></div>
<div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
<div class="clearfix">
<p class="pull-left">Materials</p>
<p class="lead small pull-right"><%= @book.materials %></p></div></div></div></div>
<div class="mb-80">
<h3>Write a Review</h3>
<p class="general-info-text">Score</p>
<div class="mb-15">
<i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i></div>
<form class="row">
<div class="col-md-8">
<div class="mb-40">
<div class="form-group">
<label for="title" class="control-label input-label in-grey-600">Title</label>
<input id="title" name="title" type="text" class="form-control"/></div>
<div class="form-group">
<label for="review" class="control-label input-label in-grey-600">Review</label>
<textarea id="review" name="review" type="text" class="form-control"></textarea></div></div>
<div class="text-right">
<button class="btn disabled mb-20">Post</button></div></div></form></div>
<div class="mb-80">

<%= form_for @review do |f| %>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <div class="mb-40">
      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="hidden" name="book_id" value="<%=@book.id%>" />
        <input type="hidden" name="user_id" value="<%=current_user.id%>" />
        <input type="hidden" name="state" value="approved" />
        <label class="control-label input-label in-grey-600">Reviews</label>
          <div class="input-group general-position">
            <a id="minus_score" href="#" class="input-link">
              <i class="fa fa-minus line-height-40"></i></a>
            <input id="score_count" name="score" type="text" class="form-control quantity-input" min="0" max="5" value="1" />
            <a id="plus_score" href="#" class="input-link">
              <i class="fa fa-plus line-height-40"></i></a>
          </div>
        <label for="review" class="control-label input-label in-grey-600">Title</label>
        <textarea id="review" name="reviewer_name" type="text" class="form-control"></textarea>
        <label for="review" class="control-label input-label in-grey-600">Review</label>
        <textarea id="review" name="body" type="text" class="form-control"></textarea>
      </div>
    <div class="text-right">
      <button id="btn_post" class="btn btn-primary mb-20" type="submit">Post</button></div>
  </div>
<% end %>

<h3 class="in-gold-500 mb-25">Reviews (<%= @approved_reviews.count %>)</h3>
        <% @approved_reviews.each do |review| %>
        <div class="general-message-wrap divider-lg">
          <div class="clearfix">
            <span class="img-circle logo-size inlide-block pull-left logo-empty">
              <%= review.user.name %></span>
            <div class="ml-70">
              <div>
                <div class="general-message-date hidden-xs">
                  <%= review.updated_at.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') %>
                </div>
                <div class="max-240">
                  <div class="general-message-verified pull-right">
                    <!-- Verified -->
                    <%= review.reviewer_name %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="general-message-name">
                    <%= review.user.name %>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-15">
                <% review.score.times do %>
                <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
                <% end %>
                <% (5 - review.score).times do %>
                <i class="fa fa-star rate-star rate-empty"></i>
                <% end %>
              </div>
              <p>
                <%= review.body %>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
<% end %>

<div class="general-message-wrap divider-lg">
<div class="clearfix">
<img src="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg" class="img-circle logo-size inlide-block pull-left"/>
<div class="ml-70">
<div>
<div class="general-message-date hidden-xs">11/11/16</div>
<div class="max-240">
<div class="general-message-verified">Verified Reviewer</div>
<div class="general-message-name">Rita J. Lewis</div></div></div>
<div class="mb-15">
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i></div>
<p>Thank you BookStore, I was very pleased to receive my order for the Moleskine diary so soon after placing the order.</p></div></div></div>
<div class="general-message-wrap divider-lg">
<div class="clearfix">
<span class="img-circle logo-size inlide-block pull-left logo-empty">M</span>
<div class="ml-70">
<div>
<div class="general-message-date hidden-xs">11/11/16</div>
<div class="max-240">
<div class="general-message-verified pull-right">Verified Reviewer</div>
<div class="general-message-name">May J. Novoa</div></div></div>
<div class="mb-15">
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
<i class="fa fa-star rate-star rate-empty"></i></div>
<p>If ‘Get a better job’ had landed on my desk a year ago, I might have been dismissive of it. Instead I was prepared to be open-minded. There have been many occasions where I turned to career books with practical activities to look for some inspiration when developing education activities for learners or assessment.</p></div></div></div></div></main>
<script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/67602d7308.js"></script>
<script src="../../javascripts/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="../../javascripts/bootstrap.js"></script></body></html>